default              
defaultHis Excellency Daniel defaultTaubdefault:default First, I don’t think it is my job to give you details of 
defaultIsrael
default’s positions inside the negotiating room at the moment. One of the most effective aspects of the current negotiations is how little is actually being leaked from the room. It is something of a precedent and is one of the things that actually gives us hope that things may be moving differently this time round. 
