defaultIsrael
default. Every single Prime Minister of Israel for close to two decades has talked about the right of Palestinians to a Palestinian state. Sadly, we are still waiting for the first Palestinian leader to recognise the right of a Jewish state. Only when we both do that will we be able to move forward.
